A '''kula''' is an obsolete [[unit of measurement]].
*In [[India]], it was a unit of land area. After [[Metrication in India|metrication]] in the mid-20th century, the unit became obsolete. *In [[Morocco]], it was a unit of mass equal to 22 [[rotal]], or 11.165&nbsp;kg (24.61458&nbsp;lb)
